page.title: 13CHILDRENS HOBBIES
page.content:
CHILDREN'S HOBBIES WEST WIGHT
My hobbies in the 1980's
My first hobbie is cooking because you can get your family to eat it with you. My next hobbie is reading because when you read a story you feel like you are in the story. I choose books from my school library which is quite good. My next hobbie is looking after my cat. I comb my cat, feed my cat and cuddle my cat, too. Cats are very clever like my cat sits on my dads lap and he pulls his glasses off. My cat eats like a dog it must be very hungry. My next hobbie is bike riding every night I go for a bike ride, its very interesting going past all the houses and trees. Sometimes it can be boring but normally it is fun. Unfortunately it has a puncture.
